description: This file defines data transfer objects related to authentication, including request and response classes for login, registration, and authentication responses.

classes.name: LoginRequest
classes.description: Represents the data required to perform a login operation, including email and password.

classes.name: RegisterRequest
classes.description: Contains the data needed to register a new user, including email, password, and optional display name.

classes.name: AuthResponse
classes.description: Provides the response data after authentication, including token, email, optional display name, and user ID.
